/a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phu-Ti%C3%AAn/Quy-c%E1%BB%91-vi%C3%AAn-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-puPwjAgB9ytuAb_Mi7F7Mg">Quy cố viên kỳ 1 - 歸故園其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phu-Ti%C3%AAn/author-cOrgi-QPA0Ee6Jo_lGkf4g">Nguyễn Phu Tiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/T%E1%BA%A1p-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-qmGc2jak4YJb6G8HvqJyIg">Tạp cảm - 雜感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-C%C6%A1/T%C3%A2n-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-MMA-YllcuQYkuLTDgqo6HQ">Tân Lương - 新涼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-C%C6%A1/author-Onk53GrYSBQGT7xscWqNaw">Từ Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/Th%E1%BB%A5c-ti%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%A7-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-cRAI8xg7FU8CadHCBAJ9tQ">Thục tiên chủ miếu - 蜀先主廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-V%C5%A9-T%C3%ADch/author-EjtGFCLaQR-cL2GZdcpbaQ">Lưu Vũ Tích</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
